# ============================================
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# ============================================
# AI tools (Claude, Gemini, Copilot, etc.)
# ============================================
.claude/
.gemini/
.copilot/
.aider*
.cursor/

# Note: .planning/ is intentionally NOT ignored.
# Build-in-public — strategy, decisions, roadmap, manifest spec are all public
# so contributors and adopters can see the why behind the what.

# ============================================
